### Variables
@baseUrl = https://YOUR_PROJECT_REF.supabase.co/functions/v1
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Test 1 - Créer une intention de paiement (cas nominal)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/create-payment-intent
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "event-uuid-here",
  "amount": 5000000,
  "payment_type": "partial",
  "due_date": "2024-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "payment_method": "mobile_money"
}

### Test 2 - Créer une intention de paiement complète
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/create-payment-intent
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "event-uuid-here",
  "quote_id": "quote-uuid-here",
  "amount": 10000000,
  "payment_type": "full"
}

### Test 3 - Erreur: event_id manquant
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/create-payment-intent
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 5000000
}

### Test 4 - Erreur: amount invalide
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/create-payment-intent
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "event-uuid-here",
  "amount": -1000
}

### Test 5 - Erreur: amount manquant
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/create-payment-intent
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "event-uuid-here"
}

